Budget vs. Actuals Report
Budget Name: ${budgetName}
Fiscal Year: ${fiscalYear}
Report Period: ${reportStartDate} to ${reportEndDate}
Report Generated: ${reportDate}

| Account ID | Account Name | Budgeted | Actual | Variance ($) | Variance (%) |
|------------|--------------|----------|--------|--------------|--------------|
<jx:forEach items="${reportItems}" var="item">
| ${item.accountId} | ${item.accountName} | ${item.budgeted} | ${item.actual} | ${item.variance} | ${item.variancePercent} |
</jx:forEach>

Totals:
Income:
  Budgeted: ${totalBudgetedIncome}
  Actual: ${totalActualIncome}
  Variance: ${totalIncomeVariance}
Expenses:
  Budgeted: ${totalBudgetedExpenses}
  Actual: ${totalActualExpenses}
  Variance: ${totalExpenseVariance}
Net:
  Budgeted: ${totalBudgetedNet}
  Actual: ${totalActualNet}
  Variance: ${totalNetVariance}
